<BaseLayout title="自我介绍 / Self Introduction - MrFung" description="MrFung 的自我介绍：全栈、AICoding、独立产品和耐力运动。">
  <header class="page-intro">
    <div class="section">
      <p class="page-kicker">Self Introduction</p>
      <h1>自我介绍 / Self Introduction</h1>
      <div class="bilingual intro-copy">
        <p>全栈开发者，AICoding 实践者，独立产品打磨者，也是在越野跑、马拉松和划桨板里练习长期主义的人。</p>
        <p>Full-stack builder, AICoding practitioner, independent product maker, and someone who practices long-term thinking through trail running, marathons, and paddleboarding.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="section">
      <article class="prose-card article-body">
        <p class="meta-line">中文</p>
        <h2>把真实工作流做成能长期维护的工具。</h2>
        <p>我关注全栈开发、AICoding 和独立产品。相比只做一个漂亮的展示，我更在意工具能不能真正进入日常工作流，能不能减少混乱，能不能长期被维护。</p>
        <p>运动给了我另一套相似的判断方式。ITRA 430、马拉松大众二级、红十字救护员、越野跑和划桨板，这些标签背后都是同一件事：稳定训练、清晰节奏、尊重风险，然后持续往前。</p>

        <p class="meta-line article-language">English</p>
        <h2>Building tools that can stay useful.</h2>
        <p>I focus on full-stack development, AICoding, and independent products. Instead of making one-off demos, I care about tools that can become part of real workflows, reduce friction, and stay maintainable over time.</p>
        <p>Endurance sports shape the same way of thinking. ITRA 430, marathon amateur level 2, Red Cross first aider, trail running, and paddleboarding all point to the same habit: train steadily, keep a clear rhythm, respect risk, and keep moving.</p>
      </article>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
